parameters:
\SE[5]Phew, but still... I can't believe there was so much
effort behind my nickname.... \SE[26]It was helpful, but
it's still embarrassing.... \SE[24]Vita got sulky too....

\SE[2]Next time, shall we try to come up with something cool
together...? \SE[1]If we can decide on something sharp, I'm
sure it will cheer everyone up...
Laura? Are you in the bathroom?

\SE[5]Um, well... that's right, but... \SE[1]Just wait a
moment, okay?

\SE[21] Ah, I'm relieved...! \SE[50] I'm glad you're safe,
Laura...! I was so worried when I couldn't see you...!!

\SE[52]Ah... I'm sorry.... \SE[38]I... feel anxious when I'm
not by your side.... Please, let me stay by your side....

\SE[64]Um, um... I-I understand... \SE[24]I feel like I'm
about to leak... Could you wait for me outside for just a
little bit...?

\SE[2]Huh, why? \SE[1]Since you're in the bathroom, why
don't you just go ahead and do it?

\SE[82]N-No... I can't...!! I can't let you see me like
that...!!

\SE[16]It's okay. I won't dislike you. \SE[45]No matter how
you look, I will accept you... and love you.

\SE[64]Lunaroa-san...!? Uh, um... It's about time...!
That...! \SE[65]Well...! \SE[46]Since you're the big one...
It's only natural...!!

\SE[46]Big or small doesn't matter. \SE[45]My feelings won't
waver. \SE[16]If you tell me to drink it all, I will drink
it all.
\SE[29]No, I didn't say anything about drinking it...!

\SE[82] (She's serious...! She really has no intention of
leaving...!!)

\SE[4]Ah... It's embarrassing to be heard... \!\SE[3]Do we
need another rule again?

\SE[64] (She's being considerate of the sound again! Why is
she so obsessed with that part...!?)

\SE[46]I'm going to kiss you now. \.While I do that, could
you flush the water? \!\SE[47]Let's finish it while we're
kissing... \!\SE[45]What do you think?

\SE[51] Ah... Laura begging me like that... It's so
sensual.... \. Look... Can you look into my eyes...?
\!\SE[51] Absolutely, don't close your eyes...?

\SE[35]I'm feeling excited...â™¡ \SE[65]Even the thrilling
Laura is wonderful...

\SE[46]Ah... I really... I've done it... \SE[65]I feel like
I've crossed the line as a human...

\SE[46]Ah, I have an idea... \SE[15]From now on, how about
we make it a rule that Laura can't use the bathroom unless
she's with me...?

\SE[46]We can increase our alone time more efficiently.
\SE[45]Leave it to me to come up with new rules. I'll
prepare as many as it takes to please Laura.
